    Author:

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.Object getSource()

      • getType

        java.lang.Enum getType()
        Get the event type.

        Event types are common to many events. If an implementation doesn't support event types it will return null.

        Returns:
        the type or null if not supported.
